# Page Shell Consistency Rule

All newly created pages must retain the existing global shell pattern seen in live pages.

## Required Shell Regions

- Main top navigation
- Left side navigation
- Standard footer

## Hard Requirements

- Start from the closest live route and reuse its shell structure.
- Prefer composing from or re-exporting a live shell page when introducing a new route.
- Do not create a standalone page layout that omits nav/sidebar/footer unless the request explicitly asks for a focused/isolated surface.
- If a page intentionally differs, state that exception clearly before implementation.
